"<strong>Start small, iterate.</strong> Configure your website and "
"appointments first, then add your products to the mix, before managing your "
"consultations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Comece pequeno, evolua.</strong> Configure primeiro o site e as "
"reservas, depois adicione os produtos e, por fim, gerencie as consultas."

